          <h2>Purpose and Scope</h2>
          <p>
            Manopause.info is an educational resource designed to provide information 
            about relationship conflict, abuse, trauma responses, and related topics. 
            Our content is intended for:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>General education and awareness</li>
            <li>Skills-based learning and self-improvement</li>
            <li>Safety planning and boundary-setting guidance</li>
            <li>Connection to appropriate professional resources</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>Not Professional Advice</h2>
          <p>
            <strong>This Site does NOT provide:</strong>
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Medical diagnosis or treatment</li>
            <li>Psychological or psychiatric treatment</li>
            <li>Legal advice or representation</li>
            <li>Therapy, counseling, or crisis intervention</li>
            <li>Coaching that constitutes licensed professional services</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            Content on this Site is created by individuals with academic training 
            and subject matter expertise, but reading this content does not establish 
            a professional-client relationship of any kind.
          </p>
          <p>
            If you need professional help, please consult with licensed professionals 
            in your area. For mental health emergencies, contact the 988 Suicide and 
            Crisis Lifeline (call or text 988 in the U.S.) or go to your nearest 
            emergency room.
          </p>
        </section>

