          <p>By using this Site, you agree to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>
              Use the information responsibly and for lawful purposes
            </li>
            <li>
              Seek professional help for serious personal, medical, or legal matters
            </li>
            <li>
              Not use our content to harm, harass, or manipulate others
            </li>
            <li>
              Not misrepresent our content as professional advice when sharing it
            </li>
            <li>
              Respect others if interacting in any community features we may add
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

